"   </a>",
"   and",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?5/57/6036?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Amikacin: Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   )",
"   <br/>",
"   For abbreviations and symbols that may be used in Lexicomp (",
